  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"site-content\"\u003e\u003carticle id=\"story\"\u003e\u003cdiv aria-live=\"polite\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou have a preview view of this article while we are checking your access. When we have confirmed access, the full article content will load.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"fullBleedHeaderContent\"\u003e\u003cheader\u003e\u003cdiv data-testid=\"imageblock-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cfigure aria-label=\"media\" role=\"group\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-testid=\"imageContainer-children-Image\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 599px) and (min-device-pixel-ratio: 3),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 3dppx),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 288dpi)\" srcset=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg-mobileMasterAt3x.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;disable=upscale\u0026amp;width=1800\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 599px) and (min-device-pixel-ratio: 2),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 192dpi)\" srcset=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg-mobileMasterAt3x.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;disable=upscale\u0026amp;width=1200\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 599px) and (min-device-pixel-ratio: 1),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 1dppx),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 96dpi)\" srcset=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg-mobileMasterAt3x.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;disable=upscale\u0026amp;width=600\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Four skiers make their way down a wide ski trail amid a landscape of snow-covered evergreens and distant mountains.\" src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg-articleLarge.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;disable=upscale\" srcset=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg-articleLarge.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp 600w,https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg-jumbo.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp 1024w,https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg/Frugal-Indy-Pass-vpmg-superJumbo.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp 2048w\" sizes=\"100vw\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption data-testid=\"photoviewer-children-ImageCaption\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBrundage Mountain Resort, in Idaho, is one of more than 230 independent resorts that accept the Indy Pass.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCredit...\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan aria-hidden=\"false\"\u003eBrundage Mountain Resort\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eFrugal Traveler\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur Frugal Traveler tries out the bargain pass at frill-free resorts in Utah, Idaho and Montana.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/header\u003e\u003cp aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBrundage Mountain Resort, in Idaho, is one of more than 230 independent resorts that accept the Indy Pass.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCredit...\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBrundage Mountain Resort\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ctime datetime=\"2025-02-18T19:50:09-05:00\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFeb. 18, 2025\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUpdated \u003cspan\u003e7:50 p.m. ET\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/time\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003csection name=\"articleBody\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-testid=\"companionColumn-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn January, my family and I arrived at \u003ca href=\"https://www.pomerelle.com/\" title=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ePomerelle Mountain Resort\u003c/a\u003e in southern Idaho to find fresh powder, inexpensive lift tickets, no lines and bargain burgers grilling at the base. What more could a skier ask for?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePerhaps a faster chair, but we chalked that up to vintage charm.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLast fall when I purchased the \u003ca href=\"https://www.indyskipass.com/\" title=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eIndy Pass\u003c/a\u003e — the small-resort answer to the \u003ca href=\"https://www.epicpass.com/\" title=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eEpic\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.ikonpass.com/\" title=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eIkon\u003c/a\u003e passes — I’d never heard of Pomerelle, one of the resorts I now had access to.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut the Indy Pass, established in 2019 with 34 members, exists to introduce skiers to the independent, often family-owned resorts — now more than 230 of them — that individually lack the marketing power to compete with \u003ca href=\"https://www.vailresorts.com/\" title=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eVail Resorts\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.alterramtn.co/\" title=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAlterra Mountain Company\u003c/a\u003e, issuers of Epic and Ikon.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv data-testid=\"companionColumn-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSkiing is an expensive sport. Large resorts often command more than $200 for a same-day lift ticket, offering access to extensive terrain and high-speed chairlifts to maximize your run time.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv data-testid=\"ImageBlock-3\"\u003e\u003cfigure aria-label=\"media\" role=\"group\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-testid=\"photoviewer-children-figure\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eImage\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 599px) and (min-device-pixel-ratio: 3),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 3dppx),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 288dpi)\" srcset=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk-mobileMasterAt3x.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;disable=upscale\u0026amp;width=1800\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 599px) and (min-device-pixel-ratio: 2),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 192dpi)\" srcset=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk-mobileMasterAt3x.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;disable=upscale\u0026amp;width=1200\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 599px) and (min-device-pixel-ratio: 1),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 1dppx),(max-width: 599px) and (min-resolution: 96dpi)\" srcset=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk-mobileMasterAt3x.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;disable=upscale\u0026amp;width=600\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"In a snowy forest, a snowboarder in a red jacket and black helmut zigzags through tree trunks.\" src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk-articleLarge.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;disable=upscale\" srcset=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk-articleLarge.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp 600w,https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk-jumbo.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp 1024w,https://static01.nyt.com/images/2025/02/24/multimedia/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk/Frugal-Indy-Pass-02-gmvk-superJumbo.jpg?quality=75\u0026amp;auto=webp 2048w\" sizes=\"((min-width: 600px) and (max-width: 1004px)) 84vw, (min-width: 1005px) 80vw, 100vw\" uri=\"nyt://image/108c8808-ee13-5db0-bd1f-db559633cbcc\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption data-testid=\"photoviewer-children-caption\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePomerelle Mountain Resort, on 500 acres in southern Idaho, gets an average of 500 inches of snow annually.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCredit...\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan aria-hidden=\"false\"\u003eIdaho Tourism\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv data-testid=\"companionColumn-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn contrast, small ski resorts offer cheaper prices on everything from lift tickets to lunches, which is especially appealing to families and novices. Parking is usually free.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"optimistic-truncator-a11y\" tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003cp\u003eThank you for your patience while we verify access. If you are in Reader mode please exit and \u003ca href=\"https://myaccount.nytimes.com/auth/login?response_type=cookie\u0026amp;client_id=vi\u0026amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F02%2F18%2Ftravel%2Fbudget-skiing-indy-pass-montana-idaho-iowa.html\u0026amp;asset=opttrunc\"\u003elog into\u003c/a\u003e your Times account, or \u003ca href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/subscription?campaignId=89WYR\u0026amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F02%2F18%2Ftravel%2Fbudget-skiing-indy-pass-montana-idaho-iowa.html\"\u003esubscribe\u003c/a\u003e for all of The Times.\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv data-testid=\"optimistic-truncator-message\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThank you for your patience while we verify access.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAlready a subscriber? \u003ca data-testid=\"log